data.description: Location! Location! Location!  5 beds/4 Full Baths with a spacious open floor plan.  Every bedroom has its own full Bathroom and two of them share a Jack and Jill bathroom upstairs. Open kitchen with plenty of space for cooking and gathering with friends and family. Hardwood floors and carpet in bedrooms and living room, 2 car garage. Neighborhood features Award Winning Starrs Mill school district, Connects to Golf Cart Paths, Playground, Pool, Swim Team and much more.  There is plenty to keep your kids busy and have fun, lots of neighbors to meet, only 2 minutes walking distance from Publix and Walgreens as well as many restaurants.  This is a beautiful home and has been well maintained with original owners.  Must See!! Will not last long!!
